•	 Supervises the external auditor, and selects and nominates the external auditor for election by the shareholders   $(\mathsf{F D})^{\star\star}

$  •	 Oversees Internal Audit   $(\mathsf{F D})^{\star\star}

$  •	 Oversees accounting policies, financial controls, and compliance with accounting and internal control standards   $(\mathsf{F D})^{\star\star}

$  •	 Approves financial statements for the first three quarters of each calendar year and the corresponding financial results  releases   $(\mathsf{F D})^{\star\star}$  , and reviews the annual financial statements and the corresponding financial results releases   $(\mathsf{F B A})^{\star\star\star}

$  •	 Oversees internal control and compliance processes and procedures   $(\mathsf{F D})^{\star\star}

$  •	 Oversees compliance with laws, regulations and internal policies falling into its subject matter expertise   $(\mathsf{F D})^{\star\star}$

