•	 Oversees the Company’s strategy, governance and progress on ESG, global health and corporate responsibility   $(\mathsf{F B A})^{\star\star\star}

$  •	 Recommends to the Board corporate governance best practices   $(\mathsf{F B A})^{\star\star\star}

$  •	 Reviews periodically the Articles of Incorporation and Board Regulations   $(\mathsf{F D})^{\star\star}

