$  •	 Performs deep dives into key risk areas and fosters a culture of smart risk-taking (FBA)\*\*\*

•	 Monitors emerging scientific, data-related, technological and research trends and issues,   and brings recommendations to the Board   $(\mathsf{F B A})^{\star\star\star}

